title: Back to School Night
caption: August 14th
description: Back to school night is on August 14th from 5PM to 8:30PM starting in the courtyard. You will have a chance to walk through your child's classes and learn what the school year is all about.

title: First Day of School
caption: August 16th
description: The first day of school starts at 7:55AM. Classes will cover discussions about the courses curriculum through the year. Most classes will end around 3:55PM. If you have any questions direct them to the front office.

title: Ice Breakers
caption: August 18th
description: Ice breakers is on Friday August 18th from 7:15 PM to 10 PM. Tickets are $15 at the door, please bring exact change. Please be picked up no later than 10:15 PM.
